// File 1: package.json
{
  "name": "sinta-widget-generator",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "SINTA Widget Generator for OJS",
  "main": "api/sinta.js",
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "vercel dev",
    "deploy": "vercel --prod"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "canvas": "^2.11.2"
  },
  "engines": {
    "node": ">=18.x"
  }
}

// File 2: vercel.json
{
  "functions": {
    "api/sinta.js": {
      "memory": 1024,
      "maxDuration": 10
    }
  },
  "headers": [
    {
      "source": "/api/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "Access-Control-Allow-Origin",
          "value": "*"
        },
        {
          "key": "Access-Control-Allow-Methods",
          "value": "GET, OPTIONS"
        },
        {
          "key": "Cache-Control",
          "value": "public, max-age=3600"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

// File 3: .gitignore
node_modules/
.vercel
.env
*.log
.DS_Store

// File 4: README.md (untuk GitHub)
# SINTA Widget Generator

Widget generator untuk menampilkan profil SINTA di OJS.

## Deployment

[![Deploy with Vercel](https://vercel.com/button)](https://vercel.com/new/clone?repository-url=https://github.com/username/sinta-widget)

## Usage

```html
<img src="https://your-project.vercel.app/api/sinta?id=292" width="100%" />
```

## Features

- ✅ Real-time SINTA data
- ✅ Auto-caching (1 hour)
- ✅ Responsive design
- ✅ Free hosting on Vercel

## Local Development

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open http://localhost:3000/api/sinta?id=292
